# Memory

- No unbounded caches, terminal scrollback, output, diagnostics, or search lists.
- Terminal default scrollback 2000; hard max 10000; ring/segment buffer.
- Virtualize large trees; do not scan node_modules/.git by default.
- Memory Pressure Mode must be able to freeze terminals and suspend idle LSPs.
